{"lemma":"مُعَرَّض","slug":"مُعَرَّض","root":"ع.ر.ض","root_slug":"ع-ر-ض","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ر-ض","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مُعَرَّض","root":"عرض","pos":"N","occurrence_count":19},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":10},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28715","n28716","n28717","n28718","n28719"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%B6"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"place where something appears or is shown"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"showroom, stage"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"exhibition, exposition"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fair"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"event, occurrence"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"opportunity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cause, motive"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"slave market"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pasturage for cattle"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gallery"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Noun of place from the verb عَرَضَ (ʕaraḍa)."},"ipa":["/maʕ.ridˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28715","headword_ar":"مَعْرِضٌ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of the appearance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occurrence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the showing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exhibiting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manifesting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the mentioning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the intending,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purposing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing. (Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatalotuhu fiY maEoriDi ka*aA","text_ar":"قَتَلْتُهُ فِى مَعْرِضِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I slew him in the place of the appearance"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occurrence"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ikoru A@ll~`hi A_in~amaA yakuwnu fiY maEoriDi Alt~aEoZiymi","text_ar":"ذِكْرُ ا@للّٰهِ اـِنَّمَا يَكُونُ فِى مَعْرِضِ التَّعْظِيمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The praise and glorification of God is only in the place"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the appearance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the manifesting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the intending,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purposing, of magnifying."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [And hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY maEoriDi ka*aA","text_ar":"فِى مَعْرِضِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the occasion, of the appearance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, which is indicative of such a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus virtually agreeing with the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY miEoraDi ka*aA","text_ar":"فِى مِعْرَضِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. infrà.] ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place for the sale of slaves"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beasts."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pasturage that renders the cattle in no need of their being fed with fodder."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n28716","headword_ar":"مُعْرِضٌ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"Anything"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"showing its breadth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"width;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its side;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAriDN","text_ar":"عَارِضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":".] (TA. See the latter word.) [And hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Appearing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also the latter.] And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEotariDN","text_ar":"مُعْتَرِضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Presenting itself;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occurring"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Sh.) And Anything"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"putting its breadth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"width,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(as is shown by an explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoraDa","text_ar":"اَعْرَضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in one's power."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~aYo'u muEoriDN laka","text_ar":"الشَّىْءُ مُعْرِضٌ لَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thing is in thy power; apparent to thee; not offering resistance to thee."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, O. *) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaA^o muEoriDFA Hayovu $iy^ota","text_ar":"طَاْ مُعْرِضًا حَيْثُ شِيْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Tread thou"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put thy feet where thou wilt, fearing nothing, for it is in thy power to do so."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aid~aAna muEoriDFA","text_ar":"اِدَّانَ مُعْرِضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(occurring in a saying of 'Omar, K, or, as some relate it,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAna muEoriDFA","text_ar":"دَانَ مُعْرِضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dyn","text_ar":"دين"},{"kind":"text","text":",) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bought upon credit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"borrowed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sought"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"demanded a loan,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doing so"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of whomsoever he could,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, A, Mgh, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not caring what might be the consequence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"addressing himself to any one who came in his way:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"turning away from such as said Thou shalt not buy on credit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"borrow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"avoiding payment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from any quarter that was easy and practicable to him, without caring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and without being perplexed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he incurred the debt without caring for not paying it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for what might be the consequence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he contracted a debt with every one who presented himself to him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dyn","text_ar":"دين"},{"kind":"text","text":":) Sh says that the making"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mErDA","text_ar":"معرضا"},{"kind":"text","text":"to signify"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mumokinFA","text_ar":"مُمْكِنًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is improbable; because it is in the accus. case as a denotative of state with respect to [the agent implied in the verb]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ad~An","text_ar":"ادّان"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and if you explain it as meaning he took it from him who enabled him, then"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mErDA","text_ar":"معرضا"},{"kind":"text","text":"applies to him whom he accosts, for he is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mmkn","text_ar":"ممكن"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [he suggests also, that the meaning may be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he bought upon credit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"borrowed, largely;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for] he adds that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mErDA","text_ar":"معرضا"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoraDa vawobu Almalobasi","text_ar":"اَعْرَضَ ثَوْبُ المَلْبَسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ait~asaEa","text_ar":"اِتَّسَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaruDa","text_ar":"عَرُضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN muEoriDapN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ مُعْرِضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEoraDapN","text_ar":"مُعْرَضَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA, [the former only in the CK,]) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Land wherein is herbage which the camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, depasture"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at random"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when traversing it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEar~iDN","text_ar":"مُعَرِّضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence."}],"source_refs":["TA","AZ","S","A","Mgh","O","Sh","K","IAth","As"]},{"entry_id":"n28717","headword_ar":"مِعْرَضٌ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Garments in which girls are displayed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a garment in which a girl is displayed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a garment in which girls are displayed on the wedding-night; which is the goodliest of their apparel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the goodliest thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a garment in which a girl is shown,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"displayed, to the purchaser:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shirt in which a male slave,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a girl, is shown, displayed, exposed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offered for sale."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 129.) [And hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY miEoraDi ka*aA","text_ar":"فِى مِعْرَضِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the guise of such a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"used tropically, virtually agreeing with the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY maEoriDi ka*aA","text_ar":"فِى مَعْرِضِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a sense expl. above.] See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miEoraADN","text_ar":"مِعْرَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence but one."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n28718","headword_ar":"مُعَرَّضٌ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[pass. part. n. of 2, q. v.] Camels ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEamN","text_ar":"نَعَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"branded with the mark called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiraAD","text_ar":"عِرَاض"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, K.)       -A2-  Also Flesh-meat"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not well and thoroughly cooked:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, O, K:) occurring in a verse (S, O) of Es-Suleyk Ibn-Es-Sulakeh, (O,) as some relate it; but accord. to others it is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"S","text_ar":"ص"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O;) and this latter is the more correct. (O.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEar~aDapN","text_ar":"مُعَرَّضَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A virgin before she is veiled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"for she is once exhibited to the people of the tribe in order that some one or more may become desirous of her, and then they veil her, or conceal her. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["ISk","S","O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n28719","headword_ar":"مُعَرِّضٌ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[act. part. n. of 2, q. v.]. A poet describes a she-camel carrying dates, and having outgone the other camels, so that the crows, or ravens, alighted upon her, and ate the dates, as being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino muEar~iDaAti AlgirobaAni","text_ar":"مِنْ مُعَرِّضَاتِ الغِرْبَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as though she were"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of those feeding the crows,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ravens, of what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuraADap","text_ar":"عُرَاضَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (S.)       -A2-  Also the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"circumciser"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a boy: (K:) [or] so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEoriDN","text_ar":"مُعْرِضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O:)"}],"source_refs":["K","O"]}]}}